{"tid":1376345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有示威者持港獨旗欲騎劫發表獨立宣言 其他在場示威者要求「收皮兼收旗」","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T11:11:45.000Z","uid":133680,"like":12,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"26f195520adf771f149f5cd50108784ae764cbb0","tid":1376345,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:00:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2338724786164546/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200954406608272%2Fposts%2F2338724786164546%2F&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wvCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=2e857ae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200954406608272/posts/2338724786164546/</a><br />\n<br />\n示威者持港獨旗發表獨立宣言<br />\n在場示威者指騎劫  要求「收皮兼收旗」<br />\n<br />\n【即時】(17:35)  在Sogo依然有大量示威者聚集，暫時未有其他行動或警方佈防。期間，有個別示威者走到巴士站上蓋發表有關香港獨立宣言，宣言涵蓋八點，但被在旁其他示威者喝倒采。<br />\n<br />\n該獨立宣言包括成立臨時政府、向中華人民共和國宣戰或要簽署和平協議、立官方語言為香港話，其次是英文，但會尊重包容其他語言等。示威者亦呼籲市民會每日都身穿黑衫衣，以及免稅一年。當該名示威者正要提及第六點，就被在場的其他示威者打斷其發言，要求他「收皮」，他們亦不斷重覆高呼「五大訴求，缺一不可」以阻止其繼續發言。<br />\n<br />\n其後他們亦向附近持有香港獨立旗幟的人士呼喊，要求他們「收旗」，並認為他們與巴士站上蓋宣讀聲言的人有關。但持旗手否認，並稱完全不認識此人。惟他們仍被在場人士要求「收旗」，及後幾位持旗手向其他示威者高聲解釋香港要獨立的原因，認為香港人遲早要作出抉擇，明白大家覺醒的時間不同，但希望大家和而不同。及後曾一度引起對罵，但最後由在場人士以「不割席，不篤灰」調停。<br />\n<br />\n西環警署外直播：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32UMyTN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32UMyTN&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wvCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=c91e06f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32UMyTN</a><br />\n<br />\n#獨媒報導<br />\n追蹤最新消息：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/inmediahknet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finmediahknet&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wvCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=11f483c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/inmediahknet</a><br />\n報導有價，請月捐支持<br />\n<a href=\"http://inmediahk.net/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3wvCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=af9c9b9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Finmediahk.net%2Fdonate&h=5011d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">inmediahk.net/donate</a>"},{"pid":"4bab9096464ac1c6a88f9b18caf0a4d9079cb6ec","tid":1376345,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e82bebf9b1156c6c7fa62b278e5c6e4bde2cd1b","tid":1376345,"uid":31151,"like":35,"dislike":6,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"乜撚香港獨立宣言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差佬都未撚打得贏...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1ec0f12f7c225fb8ddc152fb5bbc8c95aff5266","tid":1376345,"uid":107297,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"話港獨嘅一樣未覺醒<br />\n邪惡軸心一日係度就算你港獨都可以同你整件韓國瑜"},{"pid":"9b6947cabeaac3d7bf8d962f1e26d136c55f65e8","tid":1376345,"uid":143321,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"請緊記五大訴求"},{"pid":"6ae60fbb80493055290df0fd1e8b44af1cc41213","tid":1376345,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"所以話香港搞港獨真係得咪笑<br />\n<br />\n不過夏蟲不可言冰<br />\n<br />\n係封閉角度既支那人只能係所有留言功能直播到狗吠"},{"pid":"b555c040104abcbfdd1234fdeac5e29e868bd22b","tid":1376345,"uid":81273,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:07:58.000Z","msg":"唔係唔俾講<br />\n港獨自己搞一個遊行之後宣佈啦"},{"pid":"ceef3a74ac57dd5a8f75117fe71a5f9bdf099406","tid":1376345,"uid":177402,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:09:41.000Z","msg":"唔係唔比你講，但呢個時候係要聚焦翻反送中同追究警察的暴行"},{"pid":"9d3e2d3b0c7ed2a28823dc27a24a95c9e98f4087","tid":1376345,"uid":263349,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:13:01.000Z","msg":"搞到耐 原來都係擁戴一國兩制 <img src=\"/assets